+	 * pkt_mtu + 20 converts ICMPv4-reported MTU to IPv6 context.
+	 * mtu6_nexthop and mtu4_nexthop + 20 clamp to local next-hop limits.
+	 * max(..., 1280) enforces IPv6 minimum MTU.
